properties.desc: You find yourself in an almost-empty house. A small child stares hopefully in your direction as you enter.
You enter a shop, a loud bell signaling the shopkeeps to your entry.
You enter what appears to be an old smithy. Where could it's owner have gone?
You enter a small shack on the outskirts of town, clearly fortified against intruders. A pair of beady eyes glares in your direction.
You find yourself in a hidden alcove surrounded by professionals that may be able to help you on your quest.
Welcome to Land of the Rair! To the south, you'll find a town with NPCs you can talk to find out more about where you are.
